CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772910674
OL,3,CTeens who stole four bikes in 12 hours
OL,4,Csentenced
OL,6,FFour teenagers who stole a number of
OL,7,Fbikes in the space of 12 hours have
OL,8,Fall been sentenced.
OL,10,FThe four men stole a number of bikes
OL,11,Ffrom victims in Birkenhead town centre
OL,12,Fon 7 July 2024.
OL,14,FIn one instance a man was chased down
OL,15,FHoylake Road by three of the men on
OL,16,Fmotorbikes with one of them wielding a
OL,17,Fknife. The victim got off his bike and
OL,18,Fran off, while the offenders left it
OL,19,Fon the ground when they realised the
OL,20,Fchain had come off.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772910674
OL,3,CTeens who stole four bikes in 12 hours
OL,4,Csentenced
OL,6,FJust five minutes later, the offenders
OL,7,Fapproached two men on an electric
OL,8,Fbike. One of the offenders punched one
OL,9,Fof the men while another threatened
OL,10,Fthem with a machete before stealing
OL,11,Fthe bike.
OL,13,FLater at around 5.30pm another robbery
OL,14,Foccurred in Birkenhead town centre
OL,15,Fwhen the victim gave his electric bike
OL,16,Fto the group of robbers after being
OL,17,Fthreatened with a machete.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772910674
OL,3,CTeens who stole four bikes in 12 hours
OL,4,Csentenced
OL,6,FLater that evening a man was
OL,7,Fapproached in Birkenhead town centre
OL,8,Fby three of the offenders on a moped
OL,9,Fand an electric bike, who threatened
OL,10,Fhim with a machete then stole his
OL,11,Felectric bike.
OL,13,FJishnu Das-Gupta, 18 years, of no
OL,14,Ffixed address, but formerly from
OL,15,FWirral, was sentenced on Friday 6
OL,16,FMarch to three years and four months
OL,17,Fin a Young Offenders Institute.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
