FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772910674
OL,3,CTeens who stole four bikes in 12 hours
OL,4,Csentenced
OL,6,FJack Liversage, 18 years, of Buerton
OL,7,FClose in Noctorum was sentenced to two-
OL,8,Fand-a-half years in Young Offenders
OL,9,FInstitute.
OL,11,FA 15-year-old man from Wirral, who
OL,12,Fcannot be named for legal reasons, has
OL,13,Fbeen sentenced to two years, two
OL,14,Fmonths in detention.
OL,16,FA 16-year-old man from Wirral, who
OL,17,Falso cannot be named for legal
OL,18,Freasons, has been sentenced to three
OL,19,Fyears, two months in detention.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
