FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772910674
OL,3,CTeens who stole four bikes in 12 hours
OL,4,Csentenced
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Sarah Wilkinson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We carried out an extensive
OL,8,Finvestigation with numerous enquiries
OL,9,Fmade including the review of CCTV
OL,10,Ffootage and gathering of evidence to
OL,11,Fbring this result.
OL,13,F"A Sur-ron motorbike and knife were
OL,14,Fseized when the four offenders were
OL,15,Farrested. They continuously showed a
OL,16,Fflagrant disregard for their victims,
OL,17,Fdeliberately causing them to fear they
OL,18,Fwould be subject to violence by arming
OL,19,Fthemselves with a machete.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772910674
OL,3,CTeens who stole four bikes in 12 hours
OL,4,Csentenced
OL,6,F"Thankfully none of their victims were
OL,7,Finjured.
OL,9,F"I can only imagine how terrifying
OL,10,Fthis would have been for the victims
OL,11,Fand understand the distress it would
OL,12,Fhave caused anyone who witnessed the
OL,13,Frobberies.
OL,15,F"I hope all four offenders will the
OL,16,Ftake time to reflect on their
OL,17,Fappalling behaviour and the fear and
OL,18,Fviolence they caused in the community."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
